// MobileLayout
// Top-level mobile UI composition. Manages the three-tab layout (preview, chat,
// terminal) and terminal session lifecycle. All tab content is always mounted
// with display:none when inactive, to preserve xterm and chat state.

FUNCTION MobileLayout() -> JSX                                         EXPORT
  CALLS: BottomTabBar (BottomTabBar), PreviewTab (PreviewTab),
         ChatTab (ChatTab), TerminalTab (TerminalTab)
  Manages activeTab state (preview/chat/terminal).
  Uses useTerminalTabs for terminal session management.
  Renders MobileHeader at top, three always-mounted content divs (only active
  visible), BottomTabBar at bottom.

---

FUNCTION handleTabChange(tab) -> void
  Sets activeTab to the selected tab name.

---

FUNCTION handleAutoSwitchToChat() -> void
  Sets activeTab to "chat" (called when an AI UI message arrives in ChatTab).

---

FUNCTION handleAddTerminal() -> void
  Calls addTab from useTerminalTabs.

---

FUNCTION handleCloseTerminal(id) -> void
  Calls removeTab(id) from useTerminalTabs.
